@startuml

actor User
participant OrderService
participant PaymentProvider
participant CircuitBreaker
participant Logger

User -> OrderService: Create order
OrderService -> PaymentProvider: Payment request
PaymentProvider --> OrderService: Timeout / error
OrderService -> CircuitBreaker: Check state
alt Retry policy
    OrderService -> PaymentProvider: Limited retries
    PaymentProvider --> OrderService: Still failing
end
CircuitBreaker -> OrderService: Open circuit
OrderService -> User: Return "Payment temporarily unavailable"
OrderService -> Logger: Log error + metrics (timeouts, retries, CB state)
note over OrderService: Alert triggered for degraded provider

@enduml